{"tid":859934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNBC記者戴支持特朗普帽子　翌日遭公司解僱","createTime":"2018-10-13T02:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T04:47:01.000Z","uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac27fb706d55f2756698ac39f38ba2cc6ef2b832","tid":859934,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"美國一名記者日前採訪總統特朗普活動時，頭戴有特朗普競選總統口號「Make America Great Again」的紅色帽子後，翌日遭公司解僱。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上周四（4日）在明尼蘇達州出席集會，當地電視台記者邦納（Jim Bunner）於現場採訪，並戴着「Make America Great Again」紅色帽子，其間被「行家」拍照。邦納的公司見到相片後，翌日就開除他。<br />\n<br />\n公司總監諾埃爾（Noel Sederstrom）接受採訪時表示，「他（邦納）違反公司政策，因此不再是我們的一員了。我們不允許員工在工作時身穿活動的衣服。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指，許多新聞媒體為保持公正，不允許員工穿著帶有政治色彩的服裝，特別在工作時更不能觸犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181011/s00005/1539270757849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181011%2Fs00005%2F1539270757849&d=ebHhyDX2PSbaHo9MmOsjRNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7e9017a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181011%2Fs00005%2F1539270757849&h=1b6d7c42\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181011/s00005/1539270757849</a>"},{"pid":"56488c9f976be8a8d2685abdef61d34b96b96f79","tid":859934,"uid":121146,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"CNBC講公正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收皮啦左膠"},{"pid":"3aa368a164eeb2c3f0c5e207a52c9721fb4ee257","tid":859934,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56488c9f976be8a8d2685abdef61d34b96b96f79","tid":859934,"uid":121146,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTi